This app is lovingly developed by a solo dev who values quality and user respect. That means:
No ads No selling your data No shady practices
Every line of code and every animation is handcrafted, with the goal of offering you a calming, beautiful wallpaper experience that changes throughout the day, just like real life.
The app is evolving over time, and new features or changes may appear based on user feedback, but always at the developer’s own discretion. This is a personal project, not a corporate product.
Your support helps keep this indie project alive, and lets it grow into something even better.
Thank you for being part of the journey!
